16 their approval or rejection, as and in the manner provided by law,
16
17 the following proposed amendment to Section 5 of Article II of the
17
18 Oklahoma Constitution to read as follows:
18
19 Section 5. No public money or property shall ever be
19
20 appropriated, applied, donated, or used, directly or indirectly, for
